data.description: This is a great rancher house in a prime location. This house offers 3 beds, 1 bath, 1 carport. House is very solid and just need some TLC. A beautiful wood deck is large for entertaining plus there is a fenced back yard with additional storage shed and plenty of space to play in the yard. There is a huge space to park 2 cars. Located just a short drive to Fort Carson and easy access to I-25. Close to schools, shopping and restaurants. Roof replaced in 2023. Brand new AC installed in 2022.
